{"type": "article", "id": 25599, "title": "像房子一样的充气床", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-18T07:08:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133427drTtxO5J4Ckfq12b.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一张充气床，是意大利设计师 Denis Santachiara 为意大利家具商 Campeggi 设计的。充气前可以完全收纳在一个布袋里，充气的部分是床垫，可以拉出蚊帐作为遮盖。小房子一样的形状给予了更多安稳和温馨，这样那些临时过夜的人可以不用睡袋或者沙发了。<a href=\"http://www.campeggisrl.it/it/prodotti/camia\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133424QfTGyaw5gtq70xb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133425MAUy4GnBZv6P7w9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133425k7c4bOa9sCoT5ey6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133426TV9lQiJEDF8H1Smo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133426KyrQAdVUDe5NChlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133427x5kAEtpW0FLJX8wD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}